            <p class="layer__claim">More code &rArr; more output flooding the window. The 2026 consensus: <em>context quality beats window size</em> &mdash; agents degrade from bloat, not token caps.</p>
            <p class="layer__saw"><span class="layer__saw-tag">saw it</span> RTK, Headroom, CodeGraph</p>
          </div>
